1
00:00:00,499 --> 00:00:05,023
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:05,023 --> 00:00:10,527
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,527 --> 00:00:16,955
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,955 --> 00:00:21,435
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,435 --> 00:00:25,883
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,883 --> 00:00:30,794
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,794 --> 00:00:34,843
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,843 --> 00:00:39,378
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,378 --> 00:00:43,675
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,675 --> 00:00:48,440
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:51,931
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,931 --> 00:00:55,611
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,257 --> 00:01:00,635
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,635 --> 00:01:03,136
=Episode 7=

15
00:01:03,566 --> 00:01:06,733
Your mother didn't teach you
to be responsible for your behaviors.

16
00:01:06,944 --> 00:01:08,199
Today, I'll teach you.

17
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:29,633
Didn't you understand what I just said?

18
00:01:29,633 --> 00:01:31,466
Don't lay a finger on her.

19
00:01:31,466 --> 00:01:33,333
Lan, why are you protecting her so much?

20
00:01:37,933 --> 00:01:39,866
Don't disturb the Jin family anymore.

21
00:01:39,866 --> 00:01:43,499
Lan Chen, Qianqian, it's late.
Don't disturb them.

22
00:01:43,904 --> 00:01:48,033
You have grown up together,
so you know each other well.

23
00:01:48,466 --> 00:01:49,833
Come on, Qianqian.

24
00:01:49,866 --> 00:01:52,399
You are pretending to be innocent now?

25
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,933
Alright, let's go.

26
00:02:07,100 --> 00:02:10,560
Auntie, Miss Jin, I'm really sorry.

27
00:02:11,296 --> 00:02:13,399
This is all because of me. I will...

28
00:02:13,888 --> 00:02:17,376
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

29
00:02:17,376 --> 00:02:21,344
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

30
00:02:21,344 --> 00:02:23,328
♪Open my secret♪

31
00:02:23,328 --> 00:02:29,184
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

32
00:02:29,184 --> 00:02:32,998
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

33
00:02:32,998 --> 00:02:37,087
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

34
00:02:37,504 --> 00:02:43,226
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪

35
00:03:13,433 --> 00:03:14,399
Miss Jin.

36
00:03:19,233 --> 00:03:20,499
You have to knock on the door.

37
00:03:20,900 --> 00:03:22,100
You caused all this trouble.

38
00:03:25,933 --> 00:03:27,066
Since you chose this job...

39
00:03:27,066 --> 00:03:28,960
Two hours later, Lihuai International
will hold a meeting.

40
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:34,866
A car will pick you up
at the gate in an hour.

41
00:04:00,066 --> 00:04:03,666
Don't cause me any more trouble
this time, or I'll slaughter you.

42
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:14,066
Hello, Mr. Lan.

43
00:04:14,066 --> 00:04:14,966
Hello, Mr. Zheng.

44
00:04:15,233 --> 00:04:16,033
Who is this lady?

45
00:04:16,033 --> 00:04:17,366
This is my secretary.

46
00:04:17,400 --> 00:04:17,900
Hello.

47
00:04:17,900 --> 00:04:18,666
Mr. Zheng.

48
00:04:18,666 --> 00:04:19,733
Nice to meet you.

49
00:04:19,766 --> 00:04:21,233
I heard your company will be listed.

50
00:04:21,400 --> 00:04:22,666
Congratulations.

51
00:04:23,300 --> 00:04:23,866
Thank you.

52
00:04:23,866 --> 00:04:24,899
Congratulations, Mr. Zheng.

53
00:04:44,633 --> 00:04:46,266
I'm sorry, Mr. Zheng.

54
00:04:46,266 --> 00:04:47,166
I'm used to it.

55
00:05:18,433 --> 00:05:19,399
Hey?

56
00:05:20,633 --> 00:05:21,433
What a coincidence.

57
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,133
Uncle Macaron.

58
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,033
You're having a healthy diet today.

59
00:05:26,300 --> 00:05:27,966
Why aren't you having desserts today?

60
00:05:28,766 --> 00:05:30,233
I don't like desserts.

61
00:05:30,333 --> 00:05:31,600
You love macarons?

62
00:05:31,633 --> 00:05:36,166
This Milimili dessert has zero sugar
and low calorie.

63
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:39,400
Alright, if you like it,
I'll treat you next time

64
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:41,533
to thank you for last time when you...

65
00:05:49,633 --> 00:05:50,433
Call the police.

66
00:05:52,533 --> 00:05:53,133
Run!

67
00:05:53,133 --> 00:05:54,133
Stop!

68
00:05:54,700 --> 00:05:55,733
Stand still!

69
00:06:02,133 --> 00:06:04,160
I have had a hearty meal
and I need to work out.

70
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:06,368
Let go of Mr. Zeng.
Don't make it difficult for us.

71
00:06:06,368 --> 00:06:08,466
Who will let who go is still unknown.

72
00:06:09,866 --> 00:06:10,733
Mr. Zeng?

73
00:06:10,733 --> 00:06:11,433
Right.

74
00:06:11,733 --> 00:06:13,099
Actually, these gentlemen

75
00:06:13,633 --> 00:06:14,599
are my bodyguards.

76
00:06:21,033 --> 00:06:23,933
Gentlemen,
it's just a misunderstanding.

77
00:06:23,933 --> 00:06:25,999
I am okay. She's my friend.

78
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:28,100
She just helped me get my phone back.

79
00:06:28,100 --> 00:06:30,333
Mr. Zeng, the meeting is about to start.

80
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:31,366
Let's hurry back to the venue.

81
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:32,000
Okay.

82
00:06:32,266 --> 00:06:33,933
You help me send this lady back first.

83
00:06:33,933 --> 00:06:35,099
No need.

84
00:06:36,066 --> 00:06:37,333
I'll go back by myself.

85
00:06:37,333 --> 00:06:40,199
You guys go ahead.

86
00:06:45,866 --> 00:06:47,999
Just now, the masked man stole my phone.

87
00:06:48,433 --> 00:06:49,899
He stuck a USB drive in it.

88
00:06:51,266 --> 00:06:52,736
Help me check what's going on.

89
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,933
By the way, help me check on that lady.

90
00:06:55,933 --> 00:06:56,666
Okay.

91
00:07:07,433 --> 00:07:11,433
Distinguished guests,
ladies and gentlemen, good evening.

92
00:07:12,100 --> 00:07:15,000
Welcome to our banquet tonight.

93
00:07:15,733 --> 00:07:17,266
Where were you just now?

94
00:07:17,266 --> 00:07:19,266
I'm fine. I just went out
for some fresh air.

95
00:07:20,100 --> 00:07:23,600
Since you drive here, all drinks
provided tonight are non-alcoholic.

96
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:27,033
From now on, you must accompany
me at such occasions.

97
00:07:27,100 --> 00:07:29,166
Don't I need to eat
or go to the bathroom?

98
00:07:34,900 --> 00:07:37,866
Once again, thank you all for taking
time to attend our event.

99
00:07:37,866 --> 00:07:41,824
Before we officially start the event,
let's give a warm welcome

100
00:07:41,824 --> 00:07:45,733
to President of Lihuai International,
Mr. Zeng Huaishi, to give a speech.

101
00:07:58,036 --> 00:08:02,558
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

102
00:08:05,588 --> 00:08:10,549
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

103
00:08:13,598 --> 00:08:19,422
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

104
00:08:19,422 --> 00:08:25,888
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

105
00:08:26,892 --> 00:08:30,373
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

106
00:08:30,373 --> 00:08:34,494
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

107
00:08:34,494 --> 00:08:36,190
♪Open my secret♪

108
00:08:36,190 --> 00:08:42,238
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

109
00:08:42,238 --> 00:08:46,110
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

110
00:08:46,110 --> 00:08:50,616
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

111
00:08:52,544 --> 00:08:59,326
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
